com.android.volley

Annotation Type RequestQueue.RequestEvent


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public static @interface RequestQueue.RequestEvent
    Request event types the listeners RequestQueue.RequestEventListener will be notified about.

    • Field Detail

      • REQUEST_QUEUED

        public static final int REQUEST_QUEUED
        The request was added to the queue.

      • REQUEST_CACHE_LOOKUP_STARTED

        public static final int REQUEST_CACHE_LOOKUP_STARTED
        Cache lookup started for the request.

      • REQUEST_CACHE_LOOKUP_FINISHED

        public static final int REQUEST_CACHE_LOOKUP_FINISHED
        Cache lookup finished for the request and cached response is delivered or request is queued for network dispatching.

      • REQUEST_NETWORK_DISPATCH_STARTED

        public static final int REQUEST_NETWORK_DISPATCH_STARTED
        Network dispatch started for the request.

      • REQUEST_NETWORK_DISPATCH_FINISHED

        public static final int REQUEST_NETWORK_DISPATCH_FINISHED
        The network dispatch finished for the request and response (if any) is delivered.

      • REQUEST_FINISHED

        public static final int REQUEST_FINISHED
        All the work associated with the request is finished and request is removed from all the queues.
